2023-04-15T16:51:50.2575495+00:00 0HMPTP15HE20L:00000052 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("1"ms) [Parameters=["@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_1='?' (DbType = Int32)"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT \"t\".\"Id\", \"t\".\"CreatedAt\", \"t\".\"Description\", \"t\".\"Title\", \"t\".\"UpdatedAt\", \"t0\".\"ProjectId\", \"t0\".\"UserId\", \"t0\".\"IsOwner\", \"t0\".\"Id\", \"t0\".\"Email\", \"t0\".\"IsAdmin\", \"t0\".\"IsVerified\", \"t0\".\"Name\", \"t0\".\"Password\", \"t0\".\"profilePicture\", \"a\".\"Id\", \"a\".\"CreatedAt\", \"a\".\"Description\", \"a\".\"ProjectId\", \"a\".\"Title\", \"a\".\"UpdatedAt\", \"a\".\"UserId\", \"a\".\"state\"
FROM (
    SELECT \"p\".\"Id\", \"p\".\"CreatedAt\", \"p\".\"Description\", \"p\".\"Title\", \"p\".\"UpdatedAt\"
    FROM \"Projects\" AS \"p\"
    WHERE \"p\".\"Id\" = @__id_0 AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM \"ProjectUser\" AS \"p0\"
        WHERE \"p\".\"Id\" = \"p0\".\"ProjectId\" AND \"p0\".\"UserId\" = @__userId_1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS \"t\"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT \"p1\".\"ProjectId\", \"p1\".\"UserId\", \"p1\".\"IsOwner\", \"u\".\"Id\", \"u\".\"Email\", \"u\".\"IsAdmin\", \"u\".\"IsVerified\", \"u\".\"Name\", \"u\".\"Password\", \"u\".\"profilePicture\"
    FROM \"ProjectUser\" AS \"p1\"
    INNER JOIN \"Users\" AS \"u\" ON \"p1\".\"UserId\" = \"u\".\"Id\"
) AS \"t0\" ON \"t\".\"Id\" = \"t0\".\"ProjectId\"
LEFT JOIN \"Assignments\" AS \"a\" ON \"t\".\"Id\" = \"a\".\"ProjectId\"
ORDER BY \"t\".\"Id\", \"t0\".\"ProjectId\", \"t0\".\"UserId\", \"t0\".\"Id\"" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT \"t\".\"Id\", \"t\".\"CreatedAt\", \"t\".\"Description\", \"t\".\"Title\", \"t\".\"UpdatedAt\", \"t0\".\"ProjectId\", \"t0\".\"UserId\", \"t0\".\"IsOwner\", \"t0\".\"Id\", \"t0\".\"Email\", \"t0\".\"IsAdmin\", \"t0\".\"IsVerified\", \"t0\".\"Name\", \"t0\".\"Password\", \"t0\".\"profilePicture\", \"a\".\"Id\", \"a\".\"CreatedAt\", \"a\".\"Description\", \"a\".\"ProjectId\", \"a\".\"Title\", \"a\".\"UpdatedAt\", \"a\".\"UserId\", \"a\".\"state\"
